itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"十卜連囝"},{"pid":"7225e91b4e8499c60a98aff5c96122a6bfe9e445","tid":335882,"uid":36073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係好唔簡單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HKG+都已經有嘅野 你要整咩整咁撚耐呀？ </span></span></blockquote><br />\nAndroid app點解唔同iOS統一晒啲功能真係諗極都唔明<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味正負皮要我㩒上面menu掣㩒「評分」先有得㩒正負皮<br />\niOS拉個頁數出嚟就搞掂<br />\n況且Android版右下個&quot;+&quot;好方便，但係點解連正負皮都唔加入去？甚至點解唔將佢變做menu掣一了百了？<br />\n<br />\n如果你話要跟返android嘅UI設計，我明<br />\n但係個功能係你自己決定架嘛<br />\n<br />\n你令我用得舒服都可以<br />\n但係連你自己係連登大老細，android app應該係你主力要設計得好，將功能同iOS合併<br />\n但係無論網頁版同iOS版都離你自家嘅Android版都差好遠<br />\n咁我緊要提出吓意見改善，可惜一直都未見重視..."},{"pid":"1722a5d47fcbd0706e53f1960b11674c0250e73c","tid":335882,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T23:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而 VIP 一直都整緊既<br />\n唔係想像中咁簡單既事黎</blockquote><br />\n真係好唔簡單，搞左成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怪錯你了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a2c02bc60d436ee86a47d180e41ee2572cee4b","tid":335882,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T23:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>裝咗adblock但有時都係block唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，我都有啲block 唔到</blockquote><br />\n如果iOS版嘅話我可以幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340790ef698a66229d2a765f093f046621940b46","tid":335882,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy